title: Alexandra Ristorante
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Western, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A proper Italian restaurant with an attentive staff who are eager to offer vegan modifications to the menu. The fluffy, but thin pizza base is vegan and there are several other items that can be veganized upon request. Two vegetarian dishes on the menu are possibly vegan, so please inquire.
